author: hwright
msg: Remove post-commit deltification of predecessor nodes in a bdb filesystem.
All the tests currently pass, though the size of a copy of the Subversion
repository grows from 1.4 GB to 5.5 GB.
(deltify_mutable): Remove the deltification of predecessor nodes.

msg: Fix unbounded memory usage in wc-to-wc multi-file copy and move (which
